      <div class="content-block">
        <p class="sub-title">Some ingredients for our private ceremonies</p>
        <div class="list-block">
          <ul class="list">
            <li><p>Small and intimate Sacred Ceremonies just
              for you and people that you choose</p></li>
            <li><p>A lot of personal time with us, in that time we
              will be there for you in any way we can.</p></li>
