        <p class="n-padding"><span class="bold-style italy-style">Is a private ceremony nothing for you?</span> Then come to one of our scheduled retreats.</p>
        <p>See our <a href="#">Retreat Calendar</a> to learn more about our dates.</p>
      </div>
